<br>
Having said that however, it's safe to say that the mage epic is now the undisputed champion of stupid hard epic quests.  At this point, really no epic even comes close to what mages have to go through to get their epic.  I'm not talking about fairness here, fairness isn't the point.  I'm talking about being reasonable.  Our epic quest isn't reasonable any longer compared to any of the other epic quests.<br>
<br>
If you're interested EQCleric has a thread running pertaining to the quest.  Obviously not all the information is out yet but I can say that from what I read there was already a cleric that finished their epic just in the small timeframe in between patches.  Just thought I'd try to let everyone know. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ucaeadyen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>caeadyen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 115<br> <font color=#333333>(9/4/02 8:51:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1363.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Looks like there's going to be a lot more epic clerics n</span><hr size=1> I think this is an absolutely amazing change <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Go Clerics!! I have some cleric friends who didn't even consider starting their epic because of all the politics and KSing that goes on with the uber guilds.<br>
<br>
The cleric class item is very nice.  It doesn't give anyone any abilities no one didn't have before.  It's not UBER.  It's just useful and nice!<br>
<br>
In my opinion epics aren't UBER compared to some items and it isn't asking too much that if you do the time to get your class item you should be able to get it.<br>
<br>
I don't know much of what other classes have to go through to get their epic but I did realize (as much as I've had a headache with my own last piece in Hate) that the Cleric epic was worse than ours.  I don't know about that anymore.<br>
